  "description": "A stylish, easy-to-use and functional two-chamber refrigerator from the popular Bosch brand, presented by the manufacturer as part of the Serie 6 line in 2022. First of all, the device boasts good capacity and separate cooling circuits for the working chambers. The total useful capacity of the model is 363 liters. The refrigeration compartment has a volume of 260 liters and is equipped with four tempered glass shelves, while one of the shelves has a folding Flex Shelf design. Instead of the standard back wall, a Metal Backwall panel is used, which makes the internal temperature more uniform and stable. The Bosch KGN39LBCF two-chamber refrigerator is equipped with a set of VitaFresh XXL drawers designed for storing fish, meat and vegetables with fruits at a temperature of about 0 ° C. The 103-liter freezer is located below, its capacity is quite sufficient to completely freeze up to 10 kg of food per day. The upper threshold of noise generated during operation of the refrigerator does not exceed 35 dB. The device consumes electricity within 162 kW*h per year. The model received an insulated fireproof case, which allows you to move the device to walls and furniture without a gap.",
